rt because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Thomas Finamore was born in 1300, in Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, Philip Finamore, was 22 and his mother, Mrs. Philip Finamore, was 19. He had at least 1 son with Mrs. Thomas Finamore."},"et":{"1300–":"1300–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1305–Female":"1305–Surnud","1327–Male":"1327–Surnud","1279–Male":"1279–Surnud","1282–Female":"1282–Surnud","1327":"1327","1305":"1305","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1282":"1282","Abt 1327":"umbes 1327","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1300–":"1300–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1305–Female":"1305–Kuollut","1327–Male":"1327–Kuollut","1279–Male":"1279–Kuollut","1282–Female":"1282–Kuollut","1327":"1327","1305":"1305","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1282":"1282","Abt 1327":"noin 1327","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1300–":"1300–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1305–Female":"1305–Décédée","1327–Male":"1327–Décédé","1279–Male":"1279–Décédé","1282–Female":"1282–Décédée","1327":"1327","1305":"1305","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1282":"1282","Abt 1327":"environ 1327","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Thomas Finamore est né en 1300, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Philip Finamore, avait 22 ans et sa mère, Mrs. Philip Finamore, avait 19 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Mrs. Thomas Finamore."},"de":{"1300–":"1300–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1305–Female":"1305–Verstorben","1327–Male":"1327–Verstorben","1279–Male":"1279–Verstorben","1282–Female":"1282–Verstorben","1327":"1327","1305":"1305","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1282":"1282","Abt 1327":"um 1327","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Thomas Finamore 1300 in Devon, England, United Kingdom geboren wurde, war sein Vater Philip Finamore 22 und seine Mutter Mrs. Philip Finamore 19. Er hatte mit Mrs. T